{"tid":2238252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"33歲的士司機靠匯豐退休--","createTime":"2020-10-11T03:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:51:51.000Z","uid":112557,"like":328,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"04c3f7fc639f23ff8080e628b9390fc486530730","tid":2238252,"uid":112557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26402160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D26402160&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=eae6c171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26402160</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;我揸咗的士11年, 每月開足30日工, 每日揸12個鐘, 一個月平均儲蓄$17500, 一夠錢就買匯控, 唔理咩價位; 世紀供股果期我手持5200股, 到上個月終於買夠40000股, 每個月收過萬蚊息, 依家可以退休了!<br />\n<br />\n我同阿媽住自置頹樓, 一個月用幾千蚊就夠了, 以後我可以做毒L, 唔較鬧鐘起床, 日日打機, 上網, 睇書, 打波了, 好開心!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/11941/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/80%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%93%A5%E7%8B%82%E5%84%B2%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E3%80%80%E6%AF%8F%E6%9C%88%E6%94%B6%E6%81%AF%E6%B7%A8%E8%A2%8B%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F11941%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F80%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2593%25A5%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2584%25B2%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E8%25A2%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=5edbec47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/11941/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/80%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%93%A5%E7%8B%82%E5%84%B2%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E3%80%80%E6%AF%8F%E6%9C%88%E6%94%B6%E6%81%AF%E6%B7%A8%E8%A2%8B%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢宜家點算？<br />\n<br />\n33歲的士司機靠匯豐退休<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\